sequenceDiagram
    participant W as World
    participant A1 as Agent Explorer
    participant A2 as Agent Theorist
    participant MS as Manifold Store
    participant LLM as LLM Client

    W->>A1: tick(world_ctx)
    A1->>MS: load_latest_manifold(mind_id)
    MS-->>A1: ManifoldEnvelope M_t

    A1->>LLM: "Use M_t + corpus to think\n(write new manifold for future you)"
    LLM-->>A1: manifold_text M_t+1

    A1->>MS: save_manifold(mind_id, world_id, M_t+1)

    A1->>A2: Signal(keys, summary)
    A2->>A2: compute attention score
    A2->>A1: request Projection
    A1-->>A2: Projection(slice of reasoning)

    W-->>A1: tick complete
